<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-C23DC157-2B2E-4034-A2C9-8F9AB77C5F60" version="1" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-C23DC157-2B2E-4034-A2C9-8F9AB77C5F60" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">21 How to remove the <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">DRC PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 21PBA04 </compcodenr></comp>(C14)</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-0E3E2CA2-5349-4FAF-80F5-347AA9765351"><p class="- topic/p ">This document describes how to remove the <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">DRC PBA</compname><compcodenr class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr " translate="no"> 21PBA04 </compcodenr></comp> (C14). 
</p><note class="- topic/note " id="GUID-610BC863-F7A5-476F-BDAB-783E9B196A7B" type="important"><p class="- topic/p "> NEVER combine multiple of the actions below at once: 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">(Clean) installation of the system software 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Replace the Windows controller 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Replace DRC PBA (21PBA04) 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Install used Printheads 
</p></li></ul><p class="- topic/p "> After each change of a topic listed above a system start-up/reboot must be executed to safeguard settings persistence. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Ignoring this, will result in the need for a restore action and involvement of Service and Support CPP is required. 
</p></note><note class="- topic/note " id="GUID-A183FF9F-2B9E-4783-B953-787D5A18E1E6" type="important"><p class="- topic/p ">NEVER re-use a DRC PBA in another printer. 
</p></note><note class="- topic/note " id="GUID-E09EF973-FA33-4430-8309-412C166C0975"><p class="- topic/p ">Make sure a recent backup is available by restarting the system via the operator panel. 
</p></note></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Dis-assembly</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><prereq id="GUID-F8EE43B1-36AF-4F86-8810-3B686A03AF19" class="- topic/section task/prereq "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Go to COLD SDS and disconnect the Service jumper. 
</p></li><li id="LI_14F2360B54394026972652B71009438A" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the chiller unit. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Do 
<xref keyref="06DISA003V2" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-BF384AC4-FF34-48F3-9D8C-4DB12B517E06.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 06 How to open the Chiller (V2)?>06 How to open the Chiller (V2)</xref> 
</p></li><li id="LI_F76C167E3F9848E3BD0AFD08E181512F" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the Embedded controller box. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Do 
<xref keyref="21DISA017" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-AC2E7AD7-DFD5-44D2-8411-A86E0560D001.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 21 How to remove the Embedded controller box?>21 How to remove the Embedded controller box</xref> 
</p></li></ol></prereq><section id="GUID-E4895B67-7FC1-4974-A5C8-D34725505879" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_5232B115C44C4A13A0F0FA8D704DDD74" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_9BF138AF80F34359907B618BBA28D88F" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T20 
</p></li><li id="LI_15791AD052BB4049B4F6AE891DEEF320" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T15 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-FF545B02-4A65-4739-96D1-25764120B3F5" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-DA08E093-B7E8-438F-8E13-5E1243F84872-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-DA08E093-B7E8-438F-8E13-5E1243F84872-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_F7908D47DC46404A88E452344F882AB4" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to remove</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_68DA69152D0C41AFAB0ABFD7D6A27E24" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the screw of the locking bracket. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-1EF5F91D-397B-4BB8-8339-52534E5AA722" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-F437F88D-0ED7-44FB-8B87-8C7ADFEF8160-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F437F88D-0ED7-44FB-8B87-8C7ADFEF8160-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the locking bracket. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-95AB2038-2A99-4C81-A486-E7CB1BF0A3B4" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-853DDB38-56A1-4AAB-917E-23BA6F0D583B-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-853DDB38-56A1-4AAB-917E-23BA6F0D583B-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Unhook the connector assembly 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">or 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">disconnect the connector and remove the connector housing. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-7A37216C-0EE7-42DA-9BD1-0E1B2DC3926B" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-2B8E9656-5415-44AE-9576-D2CA2A70D82E-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-2B8E9656-5415-44AE-9576-D2CA2A70D82E-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Disconnect the 2 connectors: X1 and X22. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Slide out the DRC PBA. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-8AE95D1B-C2F9-4216-A962-28D82EED5FC3" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-4692EB60-4D98-4930-8B2E-2117F93E7CDF-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4692EB60-4D98-4930-8B2E-2117F93E7CDF-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><note id="GUID-0A4FF669-31A2-47B5-A4C4-51891ADB268F" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">If needed: Remove the connector housing (3x) and the Fiber optic transceiver module. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">If needed: remove the cables and place them on the new PBA. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-234D70A5-41EC-40E2-9E43-4217D346F540" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to install</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_F77204E29D3E4F6D8F3503958683C72F" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Install in reverse order. 
</p><note id="GUID-2923B9B1-A7D4-48C7-842E-99CB282561C5" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Check the locking position of the DRC PBA. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-02DE1508-C835-46D4-9296-405FB9C0E359" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-B95BF5DE-A39F-44D2-B5B5-5A97CF1BD356-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B95BF5DE-A39F-44D2-B5B5-5A97CF1BD356-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Reconnect the Service jumper, exit SDS and press 'Restart' on the operator panel. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-6C63EF43-7F31-48D5-A8F0-5338D21560E2.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Dis-assembly</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
